  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical data registry records information about the health status and healthcare
      performances received by participants affected by every type of pancreatic disease or
      disorder. All data (demographic, clinical, biochemical, radiological, pharmacological,
      genetic...) and audio and/or video recording from operative room are collected in order to be
      used for prospective or retrospective studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
